.org/resource/Austin_Krajicek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Austin Krajicek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austin_Krajicek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austin_Krajicek\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal, 38, is very much edging towards the end of his incredible career, but has recentlydelayed plans to hang up his racketafter signing up for theUSOpen.\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 298, \"end\": 303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4930554184290253e-22, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The King of Claylost his cool with a reporterearlier in the Games when asked about his official retirement, despite being open about those plans in the past.\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 612, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal isfamous for his legacyat the French Open and it was thought that 2024 was his last time playing the Grand Slam before he madesomewhat of a U-turn.\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 767, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Many people want to know if Nadal will return to play the French Openone last time in 2025and the Spaniard has shared an update about future appearances.\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 922, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 797, \"end\": 802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4930554184290253e-22, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 827, \"end\": 833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.9645868960571607, \"rank\": 0.0362956580447822, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 867, \"end\": 875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.9090629440329863, \"rank\": 0.0999557693370592, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'If it was my last on this Philippe Chatrier court?\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 951, \"end\": 968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Chatrier\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philippe Chatrier\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Chatrier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Chatrier\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe, I do not know,' Nadal, wholost to Novak Djokovicin the singles, said in his Olympic press conference.\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4930554184290253e-22, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Who's cutting onions?\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a5\\u00b9Rafael Nadal waves farewell to the Olympics \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0091\\u008b#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/M4V4uAvgNa  'If that's the case, it will be unforgettable emotions.\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The public gave me love.\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1278, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The fans supported me in every second of my matches.'\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal has also once again lauded his partner Carlos Alcaraz, whoremarkably landed a Channel Slamthis year by winning Wimbledon and Roland-Garros.\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1379, \"end\": 1393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 1465, \"end\": 1478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.9999997090399543, \"rank\": 2.90960075065971e-07, \"text\": \"Roland-Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We have a very good relationship,' Nadal added.\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1517, \"end\": 1522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4930554184290253e-22, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'In Spain we are friendly people, we like to share things together and I am sure that I am going to keep having a very positive relationship with Carlos.\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1683, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1534, \"end\": 1539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9994160668894224, \"rank\": 0.0005841011895611601, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Just simply, we are in a completely different lifetime momentum.\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's the truth\\u2026 If my age will be 10 years less, we are going to create a beautiful relationship on tour and we are going to share a lot of beautiful moments together but that's not going to happen.\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1951, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But of course I will be supporting him from home and wishing him all the very best every single time and even if I keep playing or not, I love tennis\\u2026 I will be around less than before.'\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alcaraz, meanwhile, said: 'It was an unbelievable experience for me.\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2210, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2142, \"end\": 2149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.156360393822766e-20, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Something I will never forget, for sure, playing on the same side of the net as Rafa and learning from him.\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2291, \"end\": 2295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafah\", \"score\": 0.9999718690474381, \"rank\": 2.8091163297990282e-05, \"text\": \"Rafa\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It has been great for me.\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2346, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I enjoyed it and I tried to enjoy every single second that we played together.\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2425, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think we have played great points, great rallies, great matches.\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2492, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But I am a little bit disappointed right now\\u2026 I mean we had the chance to spend time together outside the court here in this tournament.\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2631, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We could spend more time and talk so much about life.\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'That's what I am gonna keep for me.\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2723, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yeah we are gonna keep this relationship.\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2765, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it grew a lot.\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I learned a lot from him.'\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympic triathlete makes disgusting revelation after swimming in polluted Paris river  ArrowMORE:Olympic gold medallist awkwardly squirms in confrontation over Strictly 2024 'leak'  ArrowMORE:Michael Phelps reacts to Leon Marchand's historic Olympic double gold in Paris  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 3209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2901, \"end\": 2906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997100986, \"rank\": 2.899315341521043e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3019, \"end\": 3033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.405947618275037e-22, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}, {\"begin\": 3049, \"end\": 3057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.999979289406437, \"rank\": 1.318906319256603e-05, \"text\